& [SLMSlice34LiveLMStudioTransportGate] is a staged slice for live LM Studio transport
  + [slice_id] is SLM-34
  + [status] is blocked_external_runtime
  + [effort] is M-L
  + [risk] is high
  + [depends_on] is SLM-23, SLM-35
  + [scope] is add optional HTTP transport from SidecarPromptEnvelope to LM Studio OpenAI-compatible endpoint
  + [deliverable] is adapter transport behind explicit configuration and no graph mutation
  + [acceptance_criteria] is live call can be disabled, mocked, or pointed at localhost endpoint
  + [proof_route] is source tests with mocked response before any live endpoint call
  + [exclusions] is model selection, prompt tuning, or hosted provider credentials
  + [next_action] is wait until user confirms LM Studio endpoint and model are available
